  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus provides his wife with details on the shooting of a deserter in camp.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1863-12-24">December the 24th 1863</date>
      <name type="place">morris <orig reg="island">ilond</orig> South <orig reg="Carolina"
       >Carlina</orig></name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>i <orig reg="take">tak</orig> this <orig reg="opportunity">optuity</orig> to set <orig
      reg="down">dow</orig> to inform you that I am Well at present and I hope <orig reg="When"
      >Whean</orig>
     <orig reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">fu</orig>
     <orig reg="lines">lynes</orig> reach you <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="may">ma</orig>
     <orig reg="find">finde</orig> you <orig reg="enjoying">in Joinyn</orig> the <orig
      reg="greatest">grates</orig> of <orig reg="pleasure">plesser</orig> i <orig reg="receive"
      >receve</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letter on the 18th of <abbr expan="December">Dec</abbr> and i <orig
      reg="Would">Wod</orig> be <orig reg="happy">hapey</orig> to hear <orig reg="from">frum</orig>
     you <orig reg="again">a gane</orig> i hope that you Will <orig reg="write">rite</orig>
     <orig reg="soon">son</orig> and let me know how you <orig reg="are">ar</orig>
     <orig reg="getting">geting</orig>
     <orig reg="along">a long</orig> and tell me all <orig reg="about">a boute</orig> the <orig
      reg="friends">frends</orig> and and <orig reg="Were">Wer</orig> all taking <orig reg="up"
     >oup</orig> to <orig reg="see">se</orig> a man shot for <orig reg="trying">triying</orig> to
     run <orig reg="away">a Way</orig> and he Was <orig reg="Caught">Cot</orig> and
     <unclear>fer</unclear> back to <orig reg="Camp">Campe</orig> and Was <orig reg="shot"
     >sot</orig> on <orig reg="Wednesday">Wenday</orig> and <orig reg="there">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="are">ar</orig>
     <orig reg="two">too</orig>
     <orig reg="more">mor</orig> to be <orig reg="shot">sot</orig> in a <orig reg="few">fu</orig>
     Days <orig reg="the">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="rules">rols</orig>
     <orig reg="are">ar</orig>
     <orig reg="very">verrey</orig>
     <orig reg="strict">strick</orig>
     <orig reg="here">hear</orig> and <unclear>tha</unclear>
     <unclear>drod</unclear> us <orig reg="up">oup</orig> to <orig reg="lines">lynes</orig> of <orig
      reg="battle">battel</orig> and then <orig reg="they">tha</orig> put him i a Wagon on to of his
      <unclear>Coping</unclear> and then <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <unclear>hold</unclear> him <orig reg="up">op</orig>
     <orig reg="through">thu</orig> the lines and then <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="took">tock</orig> him out of the Wagon and <orig reg="made">mad</orig> him <orig
      reg="kneel">neal</orig> on the <unclear>Coping</unclear> and <orig reg="took">toock</orig>
     <orig reg="off">of</orig> his <orig reg="Coat">Cote</orig> and <unclear>drad</unclear> his
      <orig reg="shirt">shirte</orig>
     <orig reg="up">oup</orig> and <orig reg="put">poot</orig> a Cloth over his head to and <orig
      reg="there">tha</orig> Was six men to <orig reg="shot">sot</orig> him and the <orig
      reg="order">oder</orig> Was given to fire <orig reg="they">tha</orig> all
     <unclear>ane</unclear> on his <orig reg="heart">harte</orig> and <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="fired">firded</orig> and <orig reg="down">dow</orig> he <orig reg="fell">fel</orig>
     on his <unclear>Coping</unclear> it Was a hard <orig reg="sight">site</orig> to <orig
      reg="look">lok</orig> at i must bring <orig reg="my">mi</orig> letter to a Close <orig
      reg="please">pleas</orig> to <orig reg="write">rite</orig>
     <orig reg="soon">sone</orig> Dear i think that i Will be home in a <orig reg="short"
     >sort</orig> time <orig reg="there">thar</orig> is a <orig reg="boat">bote</orig>
     <orig reg="Waiting">Wating</orig> for us now but it <orig reg="May">Ma</orig> be <orig
      reg="some">som</orig> time <orig reg="before">be for</orig> We get <orig reg="away">a Way</orig>
     <orig reg="from">frum</orig>
     <unclear>bosting</unclear> but you may <orig reg="look">lok</orig> for us
     <unclear>som</unclear> after <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> give <orig reg="my">mi</orig> to <orig reg="aunt"
      >ant</orig> marrey and to <orig reg="uncle">unkel</orig> Sol harson and tell <orig reg="them"
      >thim</orig> that i <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig> like to get a letter <orig reg="from"
     >frum</orig> him <orig reg="before">be for</orig> i <orig reg="Come">Cum</orig> home</p>

    <p>Direct <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letter <orig reg="Hilton">Holton</orig> Head Morris <orig
      reg="island">iland</orig><lb/> South <orig reg="Carolina">Carlina</orig><lb/> 54th <orig
      reg="Massachusetts">Mastutes</orig><lb/>
     <orig reg="Colored">Colard</orig> J<lb/>
     <orig reg="regiment">redgment</orig><lb/>
     <orig reg="Company">Cummy</orig> Kay</p>

    <closer>
     <salute/>
     <signed>Mr. David A Demus to Mrs David Demus </signed>
    </closer>
   </div1>
